title: Tech
description: This is a randomly ordered feed of the most recent entries from Tech, skipping any feeds with errors.

items.title: These Gen Zers just raised $11.75M to put Africa’s defense back in the hands of Africans
items.description: African defense company Terra comes out of stealth with a $11.75M round led by Joe Lonsdale's 8VC.
